{"tid":620471,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"新手影澳洲星空(求指教)","createTime":"2018-04-07T15:07:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-14T06:24:50.000Z","uid":90716,"like":7,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ce6185258afd72d0f8ad706b0844d598324a4a01","tid":620471,"uid":90716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T15:07:31.000Z","msg":"上幾個星期開個post問買乜相機影星空好<br />\n聽完大家意見同睇過啲價錢<br />\n最後買左部conon 200d入門機配枝18-55 kit鏡<br />\n我其實係係澳洲買部相機 無買sony無反因為澳洲貴香港二三千 買唔落手<br />\n其實我個人幾鍾意部200d 夠晒我用 又有touch mon反鏡 又易搵二手鏡頭黎影下<br />\n入正題 咁我就影左幾張星空圖 有raw圖 試左自己用light room執過下 但又覺得唔太似上網睇到咁 想俾大家睇下 點樣可以改善攝影同執相技巧<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/07/230708_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F07%2F230708_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=6317f426&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/07/230714_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F07%2F230714_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=f9eaa2c2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cbd19a57f007d4ee802ea214a06c902acebeb89a","tid":620471,"uid":90716,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T15:09:55.000Z","msg":"再加一張神石uluru<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/07/230953_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F07%2F230953_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=f97fcf5d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ac22d8064ea6ae419d8880643235f77022ca239a","tid":620471,"uid":67553,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ce6185258afd72d0f8ad706b0844d598324a4a01","tid":620471,"uid":90716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T15:07:31.000Z","msg":"上幾個星期開個post問買乜相機影星空好<br />\n聽完大家意見同睇