\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dcfever.com%2Fcolumn%2Fread.php%3Fid%3D1962&d=dLhXG9g0xhpmkhj2B4UuqXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=77ed4cd1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dcfever.com/column/read.php?id=1962</a> 不過如果你已經走咗，就幫你唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋我諗可以試下用app check 下銀河喺邊個位再影，構圖會易好多"},{"pid":"b01cc22a607e3f497524d20a850d306372db526b","tid":620471,"uid":90716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T16:03:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>上幾個星期開個post問買乜相機影星空好<br />\n聽完大家意見同睇過啲價錢<br />\n最後買左部conon 200d入門機配枝18-55 kit鏡<br />\n我其實係係澳洲買部相機 無買sony無反因為澳洲貴香港二三千 買唔落手<br />\n其實我個人幾鍾意部200d 夠晒我用 又有touch mon反鏡 又易搵二手鏡頭黎影下<br />\n入正題 咁我就影左幾張星空圖 有raw圖 試左自己用light room執過下 但又覺得唔太似上網睇到咁 想俾大家睇下 點樣可以改善攝影同執相技巧<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/07/230708_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F07%2F230708_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=6317f426&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/07/230714_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F07%2F230714_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=f9eaa2c2&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>你想要咩效果先？有冇sample 睇下，同埋就咁睇呢兩幅我覺得唔計構圖，可能係器材所限，noise 有啲多，可能疊相消noise有幫助</blockquote><br />\n咩係疊相消noise</blockquote>即係影多幾張同一個角度嘅相，用program 疊埋嚟減低noise，可以睇下 <a href=\"https://www.dcfever.com/column/read.php?id=1962\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dcfever.com%2Fcolumn%2Fread.php%3Fid%3D1962&d=dLhXG9g0xhpmkhj2B4UuqXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=77ed4cd1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dcfever.com/column/read.php?id=1962</a> 不過如果你已經走咗，就幫你唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋我諗可以試下用app check 下銀河喺邊個位再影，構圖會易好多</blockquote><br />\n個晚個月光好大 太光係咪都關事？"},{"pid":"1c5d06a27cfc4eeaeec54f11ebf1cdd96ad57c81","tid":620471,"uid":167674,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T16:23:11.000Z","msg":"我個部都係200d <br />\n原置鏡頭係咪影唔到星空<br />\n新手無知一問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d41265f65fde500dabb80324eb03e2db9ac5354d","tid":620471,"uid":107592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b01cc22a607e3f497524d20a850d306372db526b","tid":620471,"uid":90716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T16:03:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>上幾個星期開個post問買乜相機影星空好<br />\n聽完大家意見同睇過啲價錢<br />\n最後買左部conon 200d入門機配枝18-55 kit鏡<br />\n我其實係係澳洲買部相機 無買sony無反因為澳洲貴香港二三千 買唔落手<br />\n其實我個人幾鍾意部200d 夠晒我用 又有touch mon反鏡 又易搵二手鏡頭黎影下<br />\n入正題 咁我就影左幾張星空圖 有raw圖 試左自己用light room執過下 但又覺得唔太似上網睇到咁 想俾大家睇下 點樣可以改善攝影同執相技巧<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/07/230708_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F07%2F230708_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=6317f426&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/07/230714_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F07%2F230714_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=f9eaa2c2&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>你想要咩效果先？有冇sample 睇下，同埋就咁睇呢兩幅我覺得唔計構圖，可能係器材所限，noise 有啲多，可能疊相消noise有幫助</blockquote><br />\n咩係疊相消noise</blockquote>即係影多幾張同一個角度嘅相，用program 疊埋嚟減低noise，可以睇下 <a href=\"https://www.dcfever.com/column/read.php?id=1962\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dcfever.com%2Fcolumn%2Fread.php%3Fid%3D1962&d=dLhXG9g0xhpmkhj2B4UuqXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=77ed4cd1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dcfever.com/column/read.php?id=1962</a> 不過如果你已經走咗，就幫你唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋我諗可以試下用app check 下銀河喺邊個位再影，構圖會易好多</blockquote><br />\n個晚個月光好大 太光係咪都關事？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T16:25:04.000Z","msg":"一定會 因為光害"},{"pid":"22b6600c6a72b8e58cca9f245ae011a114465bde","tid":620471,"uid":107592,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c5d06a27cfc4eeaeec54f11ebf1cdd96ad57c81","tid":620471,"uid":167674,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T16:23:11.000Z","msg":"我個部都係200d <br />\n原置鏡頭係咪影唔到星空<br />\n新手無知一問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T16:25:42.000Z","msg":"Kit lens? <br />\n其實18mm 3.5都可以既但建議2.8&gt;"},{"pid":"6b8ef50f17f0c811e3c7421eb7d37f779954f1a3","tid":620471,"uid":157720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T18:12:33.000Z","msg":"光圈係咪愈細愈好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1f609a5ef79bc93bd39f2d42409d1e7384eedcb","tid":620471,"uid":148075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b8ef50f17f0c811e3c7421eb7d37f779954f1a3","tid":620471,"uid":157720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T18:12:33.000Z","msg":"光圈係咪愈細愈好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T18:47:01.000Z","msg":"唔係<br />\n光圈細 就要高iso增加吸光 高iso又多 noise<br />\n<br />\n快門唔可以超過 20-30s 再加長快門就變星軌"},{"pid":"61b96b8b69b2741972a0bf068d687845e97b4f75","tid":620471,"uid":136044,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e1f609a5ef79bc93bd39f2d42409d1e7384eedcb","tid":620471,"uid":148075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b8ef50f17f0c811e3c7421eb7d37f779954f1a3","tid":620471,"uid":157720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T18:12:33.000Z","msg":"光圈係咪愈細愈好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T18:47:01.000Z","msg":"唔係<br />\n光圈細 就要高iso增加吸光 高iso又多 noise<br />\n<br />\n快門唔可以超過 20-30s 再加長快門就變星軌"},"c