T06:09:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>影星最好買番支f2.8 既ultra wide, 焦距短拉線效果無咁明顯，可以加長個快門從而減少noise, 另外影星空多數都係闊啲震撼啲。<br />\n<br />\n平平地整支lowa, 或者tokina 既ultra wide la, 手動都無所謂，兩個世界</blockquote><br />\n我宜家係外國好難買鏡，要第幾個月後番香港先"},{"pid":"7f2a142eb9aaf4102c22de5b6b0a05191acced29","tid":620471,"uid":90716,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T06:09:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>澳洲&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n都過咗黃金季節了，<br />\n買支EFS 24 Fm/2.8 STM吧，<br />\n夠做的了，<br />\n選擇農曆28至初五呢幾日無雲的日子，<br />\nISO 800,<br />\n開最大光圈，手動對焦，<br />\nB快門，視乎情況曝光15-25秒，<br />\n路人ABC都影倒一張漂亮星空照出嚟，<br />\n最好有前景襯托啦。</blockquote><br />\n我會試試"},{"pid":"2cb4ee5fa81c6620adca4acb611c5caae9cb23c3","tid":620471,"uid":4142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29395801a4f78aa75ea5bb7897fad974164cd60a","tid":620471,"uid":90716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T06:08:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除左去旅行應該都唔會用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>巴打又係去working holiday?</blockquote>我外國讀書咋 仲要今年grad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後都唔知幾時再有機會影極光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>我就諗住working holiday <br />\n所以唔想拎住部好重又貴既單反<br />\n怕比人偷or 太重<br />\n<br />\n先考慮200D</blockquote><br />\n其實200d新手真係夠了<br />\n之前買個部nikon無反 玩左陣就無乜興趣 想學影相 單反好好多 <br />\n再唔係其實samsung s9 同iphone8以上都夠晒靚放上ig fb"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T06:12:21.000Z","msg":"iPhone 影琴銀河咩"},{"pid":"baaca59358d62e14c0a220c9fa561f396f4fb87c","tid":620471,"uid":4142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2cb4ee5fa81c6620adca4acb611c5caae9cb23c3","tid":620471,"uid":4142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29395801a4f78aa75ea5bb7897fad974164cd60a","tid":620471,"uid":90716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c